# TodoMVC Architecture Plan
## Leptos CSR + Axum + SQLite

## Project Structure
```
Cargo.toml                  # Workspace: members = ["backend", "frontend"]
backend/
  Cargo.toml                # axum, tower-http, sqlx (sqlite), serde, tokio
  migrations/
    001_create_todos.sql    # todos table
  src/
    main.rs                 # Axum server, static file serving, CORS, router
    model.rs                # Todo struct (serde + sqlx derives)
    db.rs                   # CRUD: create, get_all, update, delete, delete_completed, toggle_all
    api.rs                  # REST handlers wired to db functions
  tests/
    api_tests.rs            # Integration tests with in-memory SQLite
frontend/
  Cargo.toml                # leptos (csr), gloo-net, serde, wasm-bindgen
  Trunk.toml                # Trunk config
  index.html                # Entry point with TodoMVC CSS CDN links
  src/
    lib.rs                  # App root component, mount point
    api.rs                  # HTTP client (gloo-net) for all backend calls
    state.rs                # Reactive signals: todo list, current filter
    router.rs               # hashchange listener, filter enum
    components/
      mod.rs
      header.rs             # <header> with h1 + new-todo input
      todo_item.rs          # <li> with toggle, label, destroy, inline edit
      todo_list.rs          # <section.main> with toggle-all + <ul.todo-list>
      footer.rs             # <footer.footer> with count, filter links, clear completed
```

## Shared Types
- `Todo { id: i64, title: String, completed: bool }` — defined in backend model.rs
- Frontend duplicates the struct for deserialization (no shared crate needed for CSR)
- `CreateTodo { title: String }`, `UpdateTodo { title: Option<String>, completed: Option<bool> }`

## API Design
```
GET    /api/todos              → Vec<Todo>
POST   /api/todos              → Todo          (body: CreateTodo)
PATCH  /api/todos/:id          → Todo          (body: UpdateTodo)
DELETE /api/todos/:id          → 204
DELETE /api/todos/completed     → 204
PATCH  /api/todos/toggle-all   → Vec<Todo>
GET    /health                 → 200 "ok"
```

## Issue Dependency Graph
```
#1 (workspace init)
├── #2 (Trunk/Leptos CSR)
│   └── #8 (API client + state)
│       ├── #9 (Header component)
│       ├── #10 (TodoItem display/toggle/delete)
│       │   └── #11 (TodoItem inline editing)
│       └── #12 (TodoList + Footer)
│           └── #13 (Hash routing)
├── #3 (Axum backend)
│   └── #4 (sqlx + migration)
│       └── #5 (Todo model + db functions)
│           └── #6 (create + list endpoints)
│               └── #7 (update/delete/bulk endpoints)
└─────────────────────────────────────────────── #14 (E2E integration, needs #7 + #13)
                                                  └── #15 (API tests)
                                                  └── #16 (README + CI)
```

## Key Design Decisions
1. **CSR-only Leptos** — no SSR, Trunk builds WASM, Axum serves static dist/
2. **SQLite via sqlx** — simple, file-based, migrations via sqlx-cli or embedded
3. **gloo-net for HTTP** — lightweight WASM-compatible HTTP client
4. **Hash-based routing** — `#/`, `#/active`, `#/completed` per TodoMVC spec
5. **No shared crate** — frontend and backend define Todo separately (simpler for CSR)
6. **Axum state** — SqlitePool shared via Axum's State extractor
7. **TodoMVC CSS from CDN** — todomvc-app-css and todomvc-common stylesheets
